text: You might already know this, but just in case: This is built on Typeform, which is one of my faves for its buttery smooth UX. Only thing I got that beats it is a custom-built assessment we launched at Eventbrite years ago that acted like a chatbot so it felt less like a survey and more like a 1:1 consultation.
